            <Title>Buddhism</Title>
            <Text>Although meditation comes from Buddhism, it has continued to evolve since coming to the West. As meditation has made its way into schools, hospitals, and workplaces, many teachers have developed a secular approach to these ancient practices. 

Shoshana Cooper quote

Turtle: It’s possible to divorce meditation from the religious trappings of its history, and look at it as as a technology for living a better life.</Text>
