            <Title>Vipassana</Title>
            <Text>There are many kinds of meditation techniques that produce myriad results.
We’re going to focus on *vipassana* or *insight meditation*, which is the process of continually noticing your experience and the sensations that it comprises. 

Turtle: The kind of vipassana we’re talking about has its roots in Theravada Buddhism.</Text>
